hopobject.body: I can't hear you very well crown pharmacy redford michigan Later on Wednesday Men's Wearhouse adopted a poison pill, orshareholder rights plan, that would be triggered if an outsideinvestor acquires more than 10 percent or more of Men'sWearhouse common stock, or 15 percent if a passive institutionalinvestor were to take a stake. The poison pill, a device used bycompanies to prevent hostile takeovers, expires Sept. 30, 2014,unless Men's Wearhouse decides to end it earlier.
